.py` re-exports `main` and `build_parser` so all existing import sites continue to work unchanged.\n\n**No subcommand functions are moved in this task.** All `cmd_*` functions remain importable from the old location via `__init__.py` re-exports. This is an empty functional change — all tests pass before and after.\n\n## Requirements\n\n1. Create `src/darkfactory/cli/` as a Python package.\n2. Move `_find_repo_root`, `_load`, `_default_prd_dir`, `_default_workflows_dir`, `_load_workflows_or_fail`, `_action_sort_key` into `src/darkfactory/cli/_shared.py`. Also move `PRIORITY_ORDER`, `EFFORT_ORDER`, `CAPABILITY_ORDER`.\n3. Create `src/darkfactory/cli/_shared_test.py` with unit tests for the shared helpers (at minimum `_find_repo_root`, `_load`, `_action_sort_key`).\n4. Move `build_parser()` into `src/darkfactory/cli/_parser.py`. It imports `cmd_*` functions from `__init__.py` (or directly from submodules once they exist).\n5. Move `main(argv)` and `_configure_logging(verbose)` into `src/darkfactory/cli/main.py`.\n6. Create `src/darkfactory/cli/main_test.py` with a basic smoke test for the entry point.\n7. `src/darkfactory/cli/__init__.py` imports from `_shared`, `_parser`, and `main`, and re-exports the public API (`main`, `build_parser`). It also holds all `cmd_*` functions temporarily (moved verbatim from old file) until later PRDs extract them.\n8. Every existing `from darkfactory.cli import X` import site continues to work unchanged.\n9. All existing tests pass. `just test`, `just lint`, `just typecheck`, `just format-check` all clean.\n\n## Technical Approach\n\n### `src/darkfactory/cli/_shared.py`\n\nMove from the old `cli.py`:\n- `PRIORITY_ORDER`, `EFFORT_ORDER`, `CAPABILITY_ORDER` — module-level dicts\n- `_find_repo_root(start: Path) -> Path`\n- `_default_prd_dir() -> Path`\n- `_default_workflows_dir() -> Path`\n- `_load_workflows_or_fail(workflows_dir: Path) -> dict[str, Workflow]`\n- `_action_sort_key(prd: PRD) -> tuple[int, int, tuple[int, ...]]`\n- `_load(prd_dir: Path) -> dict[str, PRD]`\n\n### `src/darkfactory/cli/_parser.py`\n\nMove `build_parser() -> argparse.ArgumentParser` verbatim. It references `cmd_*` functions as `set_defaults(func=cmd_X)` — these will be imported from the package's `__init__.py` initially.\n\n### `src/darkfactory/cli/main.py`\n\nMove:\n- `_configure_logging(verbose: bool) -> None`\n- `main(argv: list[str] | None = None) -> int`\n\n### `src/darkfactory/cli/__init__.py`\n\n```python\n\"\"\"CLI package — re-export hub.\n\nHolds cmd_* functions temporarily until extracted by subsequent PRDs.\nRe-exports main and build_parser for backwards compatibility.\n\"\"\"\nfrom darkfactory.cli._shared import (\n    PRIORITY_ORDER, EFFORT_ORDER, CAPABILITY_ORDER,\n    _find_repo_root, _default_prd_dir, _default_workflows_dir,\n    _load_workflows_or_fail, _action_sort_key, _load,\n)\nfrom darkfactory.cli._parser import build_parser\nfrom darkfactory.cli.main import main\n\n# All cmd_* functions live here temporarily...\n\n__all__ = [\"main\", \"build_parser\"]\n```\n\n### Migration strategy\n\n1. Delete `src/darkfactory/cli.py`.\n2. Create `src/darkfactory/cli/` directory.\n3. Create `_shared.py`, `_parser.py`, `main.py`, `__init__.py`.\n4. `__init__.py` initially holds all `cmd_*` implementations (moved verbatim) plus imports from internal modules.\n5. Verify all tests pass — this is a no-op refactor at this point.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC-1: `src/darkfactory/cli/` exists as a Python package with `__init__.py`, `_shared.py`, `_parser.py`, and `main.py`.\n- [ ] AC-2: `_shared.py` contains all shared helpers and constants listed above.\n- [ ] AC-3: `_parser.py` contains `build_parser()`.\n- [ ] AC-4: `main.py` contains `main()` and `_configure_logging()`.\n- [ ] AC-5: `_shared_test.py` has unit tests for the shared helpers.\n- [ ] AC-6: `main_test.py` has a smoke test for the entry point.\n- [ ] AC-7: Every existing `from darkfactory.cli import X` import site still resolves.\n- [ ] AC-8: All existing tests pass. `just test`, `just lint`, `just typecheck`, `just format-check` all clean.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":267,"cache_read_input_tokens":35471,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":267},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c624da95-2731-4846-aba2-2f223265b79e","uuid":"c0c9b851-0e38-473f-ab72-a955dd55d7f5"}
