move any duplicates from the top-level test files.\n\n## Requirements\n\n1. Verify `src/darkfactory/cli.py` does not exist (it should have been replaced by the `cli/` package in PRD-556.1).\n2. Verify `cli/__init__.py` contains only imports and re-exports — no `cmd_*` function bodies remain.\n3. Remove any dead imports, unused helpers, or leftover code from `cli/__init__.py`.\n4. Grep the codebase for `darkfactory.cli.cli` — no references should remain.\n5. Review `tests/test_cli_run.py` and `tests/test_cli_workflows.py` for duplicate tests that were migrated to colocated files. Remove duplicates.\n6. All tests pass. `just test && just lint && just typecheck && just format-check` all clean.\n\n## Technical Approach\n\n1. `grep -r \"darkfactory.cli.cli\" src/ tests/` — should return nothing.\n2. `grep -n \"^def cmd_\" src/darkfactory/cli/__init__.py` — should return nothing.\n3. Clean up `__init__.py` to be a slim re-export hub.\n4. Run the full test suite to confirm no regressions.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC-1: `src/darkfactory/cli.py` does not exist; `src/darkfactory/cli/` is the sole source.\n- [ ] AC-2: `cli/__init__.py` contains only imports and re-exports — no function bodies.\n- [ ] AC-3: No reference to `darkfactory.cli.cli` exists in the codebase.\n- [ ] AC-4: `tests/test_cli_run.py` and `tests/test_cli_workflows.py` have no duplicate tests.\n- [ ] AC-5: All tests pass. `just test && just lint && just typecheck && just format-check` clean.\n- [ ] AC-6: `from darkfactory.cli import main` still works (public API preserved).\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8616,"cache_read_input_tokens":44312,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":8616},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c624da95-2731-4846-ab